[
  {
    "_comments": [
      "MJ Forms admin/builder Explorer application. The builder is NOT a custom nav",
      "resource: WP-D registered it as an entity form override",
      "(@RegisterClass(BaseFormComponent, 'MJ_BizApps_Forms: Forms', 10)), so opening a",
      "Form record renders the visual builder. The 'Forms' nav item is therefore a",
      "Records view on the Forms entity — pick/create a form, open it, build it.",
      "The 'Responses & Analytics' item points at the FormsReportingDashboard Dashboard",
      "record (DriverClass 'FormsReportingDashboard', registered by WP-F via",
      "@RegisterClass(BaseDashboard, 'FormsReportingDashboard')) by RecordID.",
      "The embedded Application Entities make the Forms admin entities browsable here."
    ],
    "fields": {
